data.description: Introducing a charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom Cape Cod home that's sure to captivate your heart! This stunning property boasts a classic design and an inviting atmosphere, perfect for those seeking both comfort and style. This home was completely Rehabbed in 2021!  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a cozy living room and 2 main level bedrooms with a full bathroom. The bright kitchen features new modern appliances and ample storage space. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a spacious family room, ideal for gathering with friends and family, and perfect for hosting parties or enjoying intimate time with loved ones.  The 2 additional bedrooms on the second floor provide plenty of space for everyone in the family. The bedrooms are generously sized and can be utilized as guest rooms, home offices, or playrooms, depending on your needs. The second floor has a full bathroom.  The 2.5 bathrooms are tastefully designed and equipped with new modern fixtures.   Outside, you'll discover a beautifully landscaped yard, offering a serene setting for outdoor activities and entertainment. The spacious backyard provides ample room for gardening, playtime, or even the addition of a pool, making it a true oasis for relaxation.  Conveniently located in a sought-after neighborhood, this Cape Cod home offers easy access to schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes.
